<plot>After ten years together, Kent and Jax can read each other like open books. Then Jax's mother dies and he steals her wig three days before she is to be buried in it. Jax shows no regard for the fact that his theft alienates his sister, terrifies his husband, and alarms their friends. And just when Kent believes the whole WIG incident couldn't get any hairier... Jax starts to wear it.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?656504</url></doc>
